METAMORPH: Change visible form

Syntax: metamorph
        metamorph human
        metamorph <race name>
        metamorph dragon
        metamorph true

DESCRIPTION:
  Shapeshifting for dragon, changeling, and vampire races.

  metamorph
      Shows your current form.

  metamorph human
      Take a humanoid form. Great Horned Dragons can wear human-sized armor
      in this form.

  metamorph <race name>
      Take on the appearance of another race. Vampires may only use human.

  metamorph dragon
      Revert to true dragon form (Great Horned Dragon only).

  metamorph true
      Revert to your natural form. Reverting from human form removes armor
      that no longer fits your true body.

NOTES:
  Strangers who have not been introduced see your current form in room text.
  Your real race on score is unchanged.

SEE ALSO: wear, score, introduce
